OpenAI response for Prompt: Jarvis tell me about India 
 *************************



India is a country in South Asia. It is the world's most populous democracy, and home to one of the oldest and most diverse cultures in the world. India covers an area of 3,287,590 square kilometres, making it the seventh biggest country in the world by land area. It is also the second-most populous country in the world, with over 1.3 billion people. India is bordered to the north by China, Nepal, and Bhutan; to the west by Pakistan; and to the east by Bangladesh and Myanmar. India is a land of cultural and natural diversity, with a rich heritage of art, architecture, literature, music, and dance. With over 22 officially recognized languages, India is home to a variety of religions, cultures, traditions, and festivals.